\" src=\"https://www.fcfm.uanl.mx/storage/images/UNW6obYJU4dVS7heZaUUr25XekguiMHfWcVvJxcB.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"1050\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">La Fundaci&oacute;n UANL A. C.</strong>&nbsp;te invita a participar en la<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Convocatoria Beca de Transporte Senda agosto &ndash; diciembre 2022</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />(dirigido a alumnos con clases presenciales y que vivan en la cobertura regional Allende Hualahuises General Ter&aacute;n Linares Montemorelos).</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Requisitos de la beca:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-weight: 600;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Acta de nacimiento.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Comprobante de domicilio.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Ser alumno regular en nivel superior en la UANL.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Cumplir con un promedio igual o superior a 85 en el &uacute;ltimo semestre cursado.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Comprobante de ingreso (de todos los integrantes que viven en el domicilio y que trabajan).</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Copia de identificaci&oacute;n oficial (INE pasaporte credencial emitida por instituciones de educaci&oacute;n p&uacute;blica o privada con fotograf&iacute;a).</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">En los casos que aplique comprobar situaci&oacute;n especial como viudez orfandad separaci&oacute;n desempleo enfermedad cr&oacute;nica madre soltera etc.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Comprobar ocupaci&oacute;n de hermanos solteros de 21 a&ntilde;os en adelante que viven en el domicilio (estudian son empleados desempleados etc).</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Los alumnos deben adjuntar su horario escolar y mencionar cu&aacute;ntos viajes realizar&aacute;n a la semana.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Pasos para el realizar el tr&aacute;mite:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: #ffffff; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-weight: 600;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Descargar la Solicitud de Beca y Carta de Consentimiento en&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; color: #1c75bc; box-shadow: none;\" href=\"https://www.uanl.mx/tramites/becas-fundacion-uanl/\">https://www.uanl.mx/tramites/becas-fundacion-uanl/</a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Entregar en ventanilla 11 &oacute; 12 del Departamento de Becas de la UANL los documentos para el tr&aacute;mite de la beca en horario de 9:00 a 13:00 horas.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">En caso de ser seleccionado se le notificar&aacute; v&iacute;a correo y Whatsapp.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #323359; font-family: \'Nunito Sans\' sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background-color: #ffffff;\">Fecha l&iacute;mite de la recepci&oacu