/vimeo.com/525278159\">Informe del Dr. Atilano Mart&iacute;nez Huerta 2020</a> from <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/user135970125\">Gustavo C&aacute;rdenas</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p>',1,'2022-03-05 03:26:41','2022-03-05 03:26:44',NULL),(8,'Informe de Actividades 2021','informe-de-actividades-2021',NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe style=\"width: 1244px; height: 791px;\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zP83-P3wPzA\" width=\"1450\" height=\"813\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">2&ordm; INFORME DE ACTIVIDADES | ATILANO MART&Iacute;NEZ HUERTA</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>',1,'2022-07-29 22:27:45','2022-07-29 22:27:45',NULL);
